programme.title: TV1 Kids: Team Curios Ep23
programme.desc: Siri animasi mengisahkan Quincy, seorang kanak-kanak lelaki yang mempunyai rasa ingin tahu dan naluri keadilan yang tinggi. Quincy juga merupakan ketua kepada Pasukan Q yang turut dianggotai kucingnya, Biltz yang memahami Bahasa makhluk asing. AL sebuah robot yang sopan dan Puteri Deirdeseorang makhluk asing yang terdampar di bumi. Kesemua mereka mempunyai lencana khas yang memberikan kuasa luar biasa untuk menyelesaikan masalah di kawasan kejiranan mereka.

Peah banyak nasihatkan Ain supaya berhati-hati dengan lelaki kerana lelaki banyak tipu muslihat. Rupanya Ain difitnah rakan baiknya sendiri!. Pelakon: Nurkhiriah, Isyariana, Liza Abdullah, Nazeera Sardi, Kuna, Apreena Manrose, dan Syazwan Zulkifly.

programme.title: Galaksi Ep12
programme.desc: Sebuah program majalah yang membawa penonton meneroka rahsia alam semesta dari aspek sains, teknologi dan sejarah. Menampilkan hos Amirul Hazim. Episod kali ini Hos Amirul Hazim, meneroka Kehidupan Selain di Bumi, membincangkan kebarangkalian kewujudan makhluk hidup di alam semesta serta penampakan UFO di atmosfera Bumi. Dalam segmen Tahukah Anda, penonton akan mengetahui tentang penampakan UFO di Papua New Guinea, yang dikaitkan dengan dakwaan penyelidik dari Universiti Harvard. Segmen Eksperimen pula mengajar cara melihat tindak balas kimia cecair Newtonian untuk memahami konsep sains dengan lebih mendalam.

programme.title: Suamiku Mr Blind S1 Ep13
programme.desc: Sebaik sahaja Ain sedar, Puan Ainon memohon maaf kerana mendesak anak tunggal perempuannya itu. Ain hanya banyak berdiam diri dan memohon untuk cepat-cepat balik ke KL demi mencari jawapan apa yang telah terjadi. Puan Ainon dan Encik Ismail akur dengan permintaan Ain itu. Esoknya sampai sahaja di KL, Ain terus berjumpa dengan Ryan. Dia terkejut kerana Ryan memberitahu dia sendiri hanya mengikut keputusan ibunya. Dalam masa yang sama, Ryan menjelaskan yang dia tidak pernah ada hati pada Ain. Dia sekadar ingin kahwin dengan gadis yang ada ciri-ciri menantu pilihan ibunya. Ain terkejut dan sedih dengan apa yang dia dengar. Dia tidak tahu apa salahnya pada Ryan sehingga dia tergamak menyakitkan hatinya. Ini kerana perkahwinan bukanlah satu perkara main-main. Melissa dan Azman memberi banyak motivasi agar Ain dapat melupakan kisah sedih ini.

programme.title: Kolam Cinta
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Zairi, seorang kaki pancing. Selalu memancing di kolam ikan siakap. Kesan luka hati yang menyusuk hatinya membuatkan dia lebih gemar bersendirian di samping melayan anaknya, Aiman.

programme.title: Nasi Kerabu Untuk Che Abe Ep02
programme.desc: Suatu malam, Arman ajak Shira, Yana dan Zetty untuk siapkan assignment di restoran dan Faizul ikut serta. Tiga gadis itu pura-pura tak tertarik pun pada Faizul. Faizul saja pelawa mereka makan nasi kerabu. Balik ke rumah, di bilik masing-masing mereka bertiga berangan tentang Faizul dan fikir cara nak mungkiri janji mereka itu. Arman dapat idea dari Yana lalu menggunakan nama Faizul dan mencipta satu akaun KKS iaitu servis penghantaran pelajar. Yana dan Zetty teruja masing-masing cari jalan tempah KKS tetapi kecewa sebab yang muncul Arman. Semasa giliran Shira, Faizul terpaksa ambil alih tugas Arman. Pada saat ini, Faizul mula tertarik dengan Shira pula dan hadiahkan budu. Shira teruja tak terkata. Dia cuba makan budu tapi tak lalu dengan rasanya.

programme.title: Pengantin 100 Hari Ep04
programme.desc: Memaparkan Yasmin Sofia setelah dia melarikan diri selepas diberitahu Amar akan dikahwinkan dengan Erina dalam majlis yang dirancang olehnya. Amar dan bapanya merasa tersinggung dengan penipuan oleh ibunya, Rusdi terusan memarahi isterinya kerana memaksa Amar berkahwin dengan Erina dan menipu mereka tanpa memikirkan perasaan ahli keluarganya. Rusdi meminta orang-orangnya mencari Sofia yang telah menghilangkan diri. Amar masih lagi tidak sihat, namun Yasmin mahu majlis perkahwinan Amar dengan Erina dalam tempoh dua jam lagi. Ramai tetamu yang hadir, Iqbal turut hadir kerana mewakili majikannya Tan Sri Ibrahim di majlis perkahwinan tersebut. Melihat Amar sedang bersanding, Iqbal terus menumbuk Amar. Ini menimbulkan kemarahan Datuk Fahmi dan meminta penjelasan dari Yasmin. Namun Erina bersedia untuk menjadi madu Sofia, namun Amar keluar mencari Sofia.

programme.title: Dihatiku Ada Kamu Ep06
programme.desc: Adif meminta Sham menjaga adiknya sementara dia tiada. Afeeq memberitahu Rian tentang tawaran kerjanya sebagai Senior Manager di Port Tanjung Pelepas, dan Rian gembira untuknya. Di bilik hotel, Adif bertanya dengan siapa Rian makan, dan apabila Rian mengatakan seorang diri, Adif marah dan mendesak Rian menandatangani perjanjian hak penjagaan anak sebab ternyata Rian tidak jujur dan Adif sangka Rian ada rancangan untuk tinggalkannya. Setelah Rian menandatangani walaupun tidak setuju, Adif berubah menjadi sangat baik. Di pejabat, Adif diumumkan memiliki 20% saham syarikat. Rian di bawa jumpa dengan adik Adif iaitu Adelia, dan baru tahu Adelia di hospital mental. Rian terkejut apabila Adelia menunjukkan kebenciannya terhadap Rian.

Setibanya Ain dan Aidil di lapangan terbang, Ain terkejut apabila Aidil memberitahu yang dia tidak perlu ikut sama. programme.title: Pengantin 100 Hari Ep06

programme.title: Takut Ke Tak
programme.desc: Lima pelajar jurusan filem merancang untuk melakukan penggambaran di sebuah rumah berhantu, namun satu demi satu kejadian yang sama seperti kebanyakan filem seram berlaku kepada mereka lalu mereka perlu membuat keputusan penting takut ke tak?

programme.title: Sebelum Titik Noktah Ep 2 Ep2
programme.desc: Amelia simpan rahsia bahawa dia bertengkar dengan Amer di dalam hutan dan dia yang tolak Amer jatuh, dia fikir dia yang sebabkan kematian tunangnya itu. Namun bila Amelia dapat tahu tentang ada kesan seolah diikat leher Amer. Dia pula mengesyaki Hariz, kerana Amelia yakin ada orang lain di hutan itu.

programme.title: Plan B Ep 2 Ep2
programme.desc: Episod ke-2 mengisahkan Khai berjaya memujuk Airis menemankannya minum setelah membawanya bersiar-siar melihat suasana Kuala Lumpur dari udara dengan kapal terbang jenis ringan miliknya. Que pula seorang pelajar kolej salah seorang daripada rakan Khai sedang diintip dan diekori polis. Kemudian Airis bersetuju berlumba kereta secara haram dengan Khai, sebagai satu syarat untuk keluar bagi kali kedua bersama-sama minum dengannya. Setelah Khai memenangi perlumbaan kereta iru, Airis seterusnya mencabar Khai supaya melakukan aktiviti yang lebih mencabar, iaitu mencuri kereta, kononnya sematamata sebagai satu hiburan sahaja.

programme.title: Kongsi
programme.desc: Kongsi merupakan sebuah filem aksi komedi mengisahkan penyiasatan ASP Shariff (Fizo Omar) terhadap kes pembunuhan dikalangan kumpulan kongsi gelap di Kuala Lumpur. Kumpulan kongsi gelap yang terdiri dari tiga kaum utama Melayu, Cina dan India ini menjadi huru hara dengan kematian seorang demi seorang ahlinya. Pergaduhan besar hampir berlaku kerana mereka saling tuduh menuduh antara satu sama lain apabila berlaku pembunuhan.

programme.title: Budak Pendamping
programme.desc: Ia mengisahkan tentang seorang budak yang berumur 16 tahun, bernama Firash. Dibesarkan sebagai seorang anak tunggal di sebuah keluarga yang sentiasa sibuk dengan kerjaya, membuatkan Firash lebih senang bersendiriaan. Disebabkan itu keluarganya membuat keputusan untuk hantarnya ke sebuah kem. Disana Firash bertembung dengan Idlan dan rakannya Khai dan Sahar, serta sebahagian dalam Ahli Majlis Tertinggi Asrama (AMTA) bagi kem tersebut. Akibat ketidakpuasan mereka terhadap Firash yang kelihatan lembik, badannya menjadi tempat untuk mereka lepaskan kekerasan. Namun kehadiran budak pendamping mengubah segalanya untuk Firash tetapi ia juga menggugat kesejahteraan yang dah lama tidak bergelora. Lantas, adakah perjanjian antara Firash dan pendampingnya merupakan ilusi semata - mata ataupun terdapat hutang yang akan dituntut antaranya dengan Tuan Daud?

programme.title: Bohsia 2: Jalan Kembali
programme.desc: Tasha adalah seorang gadis yang dibesarkan tanpa keluarga dan pendidikan, memaksanya untuk mencari perlindungan di dunia bawah tanah, di kalangan samseng jalanan. Dia tidak lama kemudian menjadi bosan dengan kehidupannya yang tidak bermakna, tetapi jalannya menuju penebusan adalah jalan yang diturap dengan banyak halangan.

programme.title: Nak Dengar Cerita Hantu Ep 7 Ep7
programme.desc: Mengisahkan seorang lelaki yang menerima patung wayang kulit dari ayahnya kononnya untuk menjaga dia di perantauan. Namun apa yang dia tak tahu patung tersebut mempunyai penjaganya sendiri iaitu hantu pak dogol. Untuk melepaskan diri dari Hantu pak dogol dia harus menjalani beberapa ritual apatah lagi dia melanggar pantang dengan berkahwin dengan gadis yang bukan satu keturunan.

programme.title: The Cave
programme.desc: Selepas sekumpulan ahli biologi menemui rangkaian besar gua yang belum diterokai di Romania dan, mempercayai ia sebagai ekosistem yang tidak terganggu yang telah menghasilkan spesies baharu, mereka mengupah pasukan peneroka gua bawah air terbaik Amerika di dunia. Semasa meneroka lebih dalam ke dalam gua bawah air, gelongsor batu menghalang pintu keluar mereka, dan tidak lama kemudian mereka menemui makhluk karnivor yang lebih besar telah menambahkannya ke rantai makanannya.

Berlumba-lumba di jalanan, kejar-mengejar, berkonvoi dan disaman oleh polis telah menjadi rasa masam dalam kehidupan mereka yang berkongsi minat yang sama.

Haikal dengan rasa ingin tahu masuk ke dalam hutan bersama Imran untuk menjejaki lokasi seperti di dalam peta tersebut manakala Sohot dan Salim dilihat mengekori mereka

programme.title: Awoken
programme.desc: Apabila tiada apa yang boleh dilakukan untuk pesakit Insomnia Fatal Familial di hospital, seorang pelajar perubatan telah menyuruh abangnya dipindahkan ke kemudahan rahsia di ruang bawah tanah untuk rawatan alternatif.

programme.title: You Saka… Pergi Jauh-jauh Ep 13 Ep13
programme.desc: Ibrahim, Nia dan Adrus mencari Shasa dan akhirnya dapat menemuinya dalam keadaan bertelingkahlaku dan mengamal budaya kelompok 'punk' yang diapit dan dibawa lari oleh Zeti yang memiliki dan mengamalkan budaya yang diresapi oleh Gelam. Mereka gagal menyelamatkan Shasa, sebaliknya Adrus dicederakan dan dirasuk oleh Zeti hingga tidak sedar diri. Dalam pada itu Gelam terus menemui Zeti dan mereka bertelingkah gara-gara Gelam tidak puas hati tindakannya. Dalam kekusutan Nia, semasa dia ke bandar tiba-tiba menemui Tok Alai. Dalam hubungan ini, tepat pada masanya di mana dengan bantuannya dia menasihati Ibrahim serta ahli keluarga yang lain tentang cara-cara berusaha untuk mengubati penyakit Adrus berlandaskan Islam. Nia yang berkelebihan dalam usahanya berfikir telah diberi petunjuk lokasi Shasa dan akhirnya bersama Ibrahim dan bantuan Tok Alai, Shasa berjaya diselamatkan dari rumah Zeti. Adrus masih tidak sedarkan diri

programme.title: Hutang 2D
programme.desc: Mengisahkan seorang pelukis webtoon yang kuat berangan dan pengecut bernama Ayie yang mempunyai dua masalah dalam hidupnya iaitu hutang bapanya dan cinta terpendamnya pada Shima. Kehadiran dua gangster iaitu Han dan Kit menambahkan satu lagi masalah dalam hidupnya. Segalanya berubah melalui tablet ajaib di mana segala lukisannya menjadi hidup.

programme.title: Model Family Ep 1 Ep1
programme.desc: Sebuah keluarga ibu bapa tunggal (Yu Xiang dan Tong Tong) berpindah ke kawasan kejiranan baharu di mana kehidupan semua orang nampak sempurna. Walau bagaimanapun, keadaan mungkin kelihatan cerah di luar, rahsia gelap dan seram menyerbu setiap keluarga dari dalam, dan tidak ada yang benar-benar seperti yang kelihatan.

programme.title: Sebelum Titik Noktah Ep 2 Ep2
programme.desc: Amelia simpan rahsia bahawa dia bertengkar dengan Amer di dalam hutan dan dia yang tolak Amer jatuh, dia fikir dia yang sebabkan kematian tunangnya itu. Namun bila Amelia dapat tahu tentang ada kesan seolah diikat leher Amer. Dia pula mengesyaki Hariz, kerana Amelia yakin ada orang lain di hutan itu.

programme.title: Galaxy Games
programme.desc: Sekumpulan orang dewasa muda dihantar ke planet yang jauh untuk bersaing dalam permainan Sol Invictus yang berprestij.

programme.title: Sebelum Titik Noktah Ep 2 Ep2
programme.desc: Amelia simpan rahsia bahawa dia bertengkar dengan Amer di dalam hutan dan dia yang tolak Amer jatuh, dia fikir dia yang sebabkan kematian tunangnya itu. programme.title: Plan B Ep 2 Ep2
programme.desc: Episod ke-2 mengisahkan Khai berjaya memujuk Airis menemankannya minum setelah membawanya bersiar-siar melihat suasana Kuala Lumpur dari udara dengan kapal terbang jenis ringan miliknya. Que pula seorang pelajar kolej salah seorang daripada rakan Khai sedang diintip dan diekori polis. Kemudian Airis bersetuju berlumba kereta secara haram dengan Khai, sebagai satu syarat untuk keluar bagi kali kedua bersama-sama minum dengannya. Setelah Khai memenangi perlumbaan kereta iru, Airis seterusnya mencabar Khai supaya melakukan aktiviti yang lebih mencabar, iaitu mencuri kereta, kononnya sematamata sebagai satu hiburan sahaja.

programme.title: Bohsia 2: Jalan Kembali
programme.desc: Tasha adalah seorang gadis yang dibesarkan tanpa keluarga dan pendidikan, memaksanya untuk mencari perlindungan di dunia bawah tanah, di kalangan samseng jalanan. Dia tidak lama kemudian menjadi bosan dengan kehidupannya yang tidak bermakna, tetapi jalannya menuju penebusan adalah jalan yang diturap dengan banyak halangan.

programme.title: Sebelum Titik Noktah Ep 2 Ep2
programme.desc: Amelia simpan rahsia bahawa dia bertengkar dengan Amer di dalam hutan dan dia yang tolak Amer jatuh, dia fikir dia yang sebabkan kematian tunangnya itu. programme.title: Dorm
programme.desc: Ton (Chalee Trairat) ialah seorang budak lelaki Thai yang dihantar oleh bapanya (Suttipong Tudpitakkul) ke sekolah berasrama penuh untuk mendapatkan pendidikan yang lebih teratur. Setiba di sana, rakan sekolahnya mengusiknya dengan cerita hantu yang menakutkan tentang seorang budak lelaki yang lemas di kolam renang, dan seorang gadis yang membunuh diri. Ton sukar untuk menumpukan perhatian di sekolah kerana rakan sekelasnya yang baru, tetapi tidak lama kemudian dia berkawan dengan Vichien (Siranath Jianthavorn) bahawa kawan barunya ialah budak lelaki yang lemas.

programme.title: Siksa
programme.desc: Seorang gadis bernama Aniza sering menyanyi di majlis-majlis perkahwinan di kampung itu. Aniza mempunyai seorang kekasih bernama Jalal yang sering menjadi pasangan duetnya semasa menyanyi. Aniza berasa kecewa setelah dia mengetahui rupa-rupanya Jalal adalah seorang kaki judi. Setelah dipujuk, Aniza bersetuju untuk berkahwin dengan Jalal yang berjanji tidak akan berjudi lagi. Namun, setelah beberapa tahun mereka berkahwin Jalal masih tidak dapat meninggalkan tabiatnya yang gemar berjudi sehingga membuatkan rumah tangganya dengan Aniza retak akibat banyak hutang.

programme.title: Hanya Kawan
programme.desc: Hans dan Ella merupakan pasangan kekasih yang masing-masing memasang impian untuk menjadi pelakon dan penyanyi yang berjaya suatu hari nanti. Ella yang ditemui seorang penerbit lagu, Michael Nasir mula mencapai kejayaan terlebih dahulu. Percaya akan kebolehan Ella, dia ditawarkan untuk menyertai syarikat rakamannya. Hubungan antara Hans dan Ella mula menghadapi masalah apabila Ella kelihatan semakin rapat dengan Michael dan makin berjaya manakala Hnas masih mencari-cari arah sebagai seorang pelakon.

programme.title: Komik
programme.desc: Samad bekerja sebagai pelukis komik di sebuah syarikat. Dia selalu sibuk dengan kerjanya sehingga sering mengabaikan keluarga dan tunangnya. Pada suatu malam, Samad terlibat dalam satu kemalangan jalan raya. Apabila tersedar daripada pengsan, Samad bertemu dengan Adika, watak hero dalam komik yang dicipta olehnya. Samad menyedari bahawa dia secara tidak sengaja telah termasuk ke dalam dunia komik ciptaannya itu. Dalam masa yang sama, Adika meminta bantuan daripada Samad untuk menghadapi ancaman daripada Jalak, watak penjahat dalam komik itu. Berjayakah Samad membantu Adika dan seterusnya mencari jalan keluar untuk kembali ke dunia nyata?

programme.title: Mr Cinderella
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Puteri Megawati, puteri mahkota negara Inderapuri yang mengalami kecederaan dalam satu kemalangan jalanraya telah diselamatkan oleh Hakimi. Semasa meninggalkan tempat kemalangan itu, Hakimi secara tidak sengaja tercicir sebelah kasut yang dipinjam daripada sahabatnya, Kumin. Oleh kerana berasa terhutang budi kepada penyelamatnya, Puteri Megawati meminta pertolongan seorang wartawan untuk mencari Mr Cinderella yang menyelamatkannya dengan ganjaran lumayan.

programme.title: Cinta Buta
programme.desc: Dr. Razlan, seorang pensyarah buta di Akademi Matahati di mana para pelajarnya terdiri daripada golongan cacat penglihatan. Dengan bantuan Aida, dia berusaha keras membantu golongan ini supaya berjaya di masa hadapan. Abas, tunang kepada Aida kurang senang dengan perihal itu kerana Aida sering bersama Dr. Razlan ketika bekerja. Abas ingin mempercepatkan perkahwinannya dengan Aida namun berlaku sebaliknya apabila Aida semakin tertarik hati dengan Dr. Razlan.

programme.title: Sejati
programme.desc: Bani, seorang lepasan universiti telah tercedera dalam satu perlumbaan motosikal haram. Semasa mendapat rawatan di hospital, doktor mendapati Bani sedang menghidap penyakit kanser paru-paru yang serius. Dia ke Cameron Highlands untuk berehat dan di situ dia bertemu dengan Haryati yang menghidap penyakit leukimia lalu saling jatuh cinta.

programme.title: Arbaie Bujang Kembali
programme.desc: Semasa isterinya bersalin anak ketiga, Arbaie mengambil kesempatan untuk keluar berfoya-foya dengan rakan-rakannya, Mat Nor dan Ajmain. Arbaie kemudiannya jatuh cinta dengan seorang wanita bernama Nab. Untuk mengelakkan kegiatannya terbongkar, Arbaie mencari helah untuk menghantar isterinya pulang ke kampung. Perbuatan Arbaie itu telah menimbulkan pelbagai masalah kepada dirinya di kemudian hari.

programme.title: Si Badol
programme.desc: Perjuangan kelas pekerja digambarkan apabila kapitalisme semakin mendapat tempat di dunia. Badol, seorang penipu, menyamar menjadi orang kaya yang datang dari Sarawak lalu mengahwini Milah. Tipu helah digunakannya untuk memperdaya orang kaya. Modus operandinya adalah dengan meminjam wang yang banyak. Badol pun pergi menghilangkan diri setelah berjaya memperdaya orang kaya.

programme.desc: Seorang gadis bernama Aniza sering menyanyi di majlis-majlis perkahwinan di kampung itu. Dalam masa yang sama, seorang wanita bernama Anisah jatuh hati kepada Hakimi. Dia menawarkan pekerjaan kepada Hakimi di syarikatnya dan pelbagai konflik berlaku di antara Hakimi, Puteri Megawati dan Anisah.

programme.desc: Mengisahkan Ujang yang tinggal bersama datuk setelah bapanya meninggal dunia. Ujang ingin berkahwin dengan Milah. Namun, dia malas bekerja dan hanya mengharapkan harta datuknya sahaja. Pada suatu hari, datuk Ujang menyatakan bahawa dia akan berkahwin dengan seseorang. Although Siou-Ying was betrayed by You-Tsai, she has still been a dutiful daughter to her mother-in-law, and has single-mindedly raised four children.

programme.desc: The beauty of folklore is all around us in Taiwan, but we often overlook it and fail to appreciate and feel it. The aim of this program is to promote the beauty of Taiwanese folklore and bring folklore to life. This program showcases folk culture regardless of race or religion, and presents travel information in a fun way, combining easy-to-understand folk culture knowledge with the mission of passing on folk culture. The audience can learn more about folk cultural products such as handicrafts, antiques, temple folklore, as well as short stories about the gods, and information about local tourism. It is an educational and entertaining way to travel and learn about folklore.

programme.title: From Vegas To Macau II
programme.desc: Mark, the chief accountant of a money-laundering syndicate, has stolen US$15 billion from the fund and absconded to Thailand with his daughter. Interpol agent Lok seeks help from Ken, the God of Gamblers, to capture the syndicates mastermind. As they search for Mark to testify in the case, Ken reunites with the love of his life

programme.title: Flashover
programme.desc: This is based on a true story. A sudden earthquake hits the gas pipes in an industrial park, triggering massive explosions and engulfing the neighboring area in flames. When the Fire Rescue Force reaches the scene, firefighters must fight against the flames and time, as they commit to safeguard lives with their own.

programme.title: Secret Diary of a Mom To Be, The
programme.desc: A high-flying PR manager and her loving husband swear by a childless lifestyle but she is shocked to learn that she is expecting just when things look bright for a promotion! How would they deal with the unexpected surprises that life throws in their way?

programme.title: Bullet and Brain
programme.desc: Nine years ago, two legendary criminals, Bullet and Brain, vowed not to kill and lie before they disappeared. Both now return for a mission - to protect the granddaughter of the triad boss. Can they succeed without breaking their vows?

programme.title: Touch of the Light
programme.desc: A blind but talented pianist Siang encounters an unrecognized but skilful dancer Chieh. Chieh is attracted to the courageous Siang while Siang is fascinated by the adventurous Chieh. Their friendship grows as Siang and Chieh pursue their dreams together. Sandrine Pinna was awarded Best Actress for her role as Chieh in the 2012 Taipei Film Festival.

programme.title: Endless Battle
programme.desc: This is a story about two brothers. The younger brother is a drug lord while the elder brother Zhong is a police officer in the Narcotics Bureau. Both are involved in a drug cartels turf battle and during an escort mission, Zhong discovers his brothers hidden identity. This leads to an endless battle between good and evil.

programme.title: The Mermaid
programme.desc: A real estate tycoon plans to turn a marine protected area into a new property development, thereby destroying the secret habitat of the mermaids. A beautiful mermaid, Shan, is tasked to seduce the tycoon and stop the destruction. However, when Shans mission fails, a final, fatal war between humans and mermaids becomes inevitable.

programme.title: The Moon Thieves
programme.desc: A crooked watch dealer assembles a daring crew - a thief, an explosive expert, a lock breaker and a watch connoisseur - to steal three luxury watches in Tokyo. Their mission takes an unexpected turn when they discover the legendary 'Moonwatch.' Pursued by the yakuza, the team must unite to navigate the chaos and pull off their high-stakes heist.

programme.title: Ready O/R Rot
programme.desc: Guy and Heidi are finally getting married but pressure from Guys mother creates much friction between them. Meanwhile, Grey Bear suspects his wife of cheating on him and Ken faces the biggest crisis of his life when Jessica accidentally gets pregnant. Can they eventually solve their relationship problems?

programme.title: Death Stranding
programme.desc: To overhaul the underground gambling industry, the police join hands with the gambling association to crack down on illegal casinos. They auction off new casino licenses to regulate the industry, but this results in an upheaval in the gambling world, unveiling the hidden interests and secrets while sparking conflicts between gangs...

programme.title: American Dreams in China
programme.desc: During the economic reform period in the 80s, three undergraduates are brought together by a common ambition to live the American dream.

programme.title: The Fatal Raid
programme.desc: Twenty years after a deadly bloodbath between the Hong Kong Police and Macau gangsters, Madam Fong, the surviving team member, leads a new squad of four policewomen across borders to pursue young anarchists terrorizing Macau in a mission to protect the Hong Kong Polices Deputy Chief Commissioner.

programme.title: Knockout
programme.desc: A former boxing champion and convict who has just been released from prison discovers that his wife has died and he is now a single parent. The situation is made worse with his daughters diagnosis of leukaemia. In order to encourage his daughter and fulfil his promise of never giving up, he re-enters the boxing ring.

programme.title: Once Upon a Time in Hong Kong
programme.desc: This is a story of ICAC investigators fighting against rampant corruption in early 1970s Hong Kong. A police sergeant teams up with a triad boss to make billions of dollars in bribes. As a lawyer joins his friend in ICAC to investigate their collusion and fight against corruption, the battle between the righteous and the wicked has just begun.

programme.title: The Mermaid
programme.desc: A real estate tycoon plans to turn a marine protected area into a new property development, thereby destroying the secret habitat of the mermaids. A beautiful mermaid, Shan, is tasked to seduce the tycoon and stop the destruction. However, when Shans mission fails, a final, fatal war between humans and mermaids becomes inevitable.

programme.title: Mr. Long
programme.desc: A Taiwanese hitman Mr. Long escapes from the triad after his assignment in Tokyo gone awry. He encounters a Taiwanese woman and her son and the three of them start a new life together. Unfortunately, Mr. Long is being pursued by the triad again

programme.title: You are the One
programme.desc: A talented rogue trader experiences a 180-degree change in life when he encounters a girl who does not believe good things will happen to her. Will they fall in love? It seems like a Cinderellas adventure has just begun!

programme.title: Imprisoned 2: There Is No Escape From Fate
programme.desc: Hong Kong businessman Yu and his secretary travel abroad for business meetings. When the secretary is killed in their hotel, Yu is arrested. Despite pleading not guilty, Yu is imprisoned in a cruel multinational prison where the warden enjoys torturing prisoners, and he must find a way to escape from this dark and deadly prison to survive.

programme.title: Mama's Affair
programme.desc: Former talent manager Mei Fung stays home to take care of her husband and son after retirement. She decides to re-enter the entertainment business to find her value in life, and successfully transforms a local restaurant delivery boy, Fong Ching, into a young pop idol. This makes her teenage son, Jonathan, intensely jealous of Fong Ching.

programme.title: As It Burns
programme.desc: Detective Wei investigates the death of Yan Zhen in an explosion which seems more than an accident to him. Wei then finds out that Yan Zhen looks a lot like Yin, the girlfriend of Yan Zhens childhood friend Lu, and uncovers a tangled web of deceit leading to surprising revelations when he merges details from the past and the present.

programme.title: Lion Rock
programme.desc: Based on the true story of David Ki, one of Asias top rock climbers who lost everything when a motorcycle accident crippled him. Rather than succumbing to his fate, David found a way of scaling the dizzying peaks again by becoming a wheelchair-bound athlete and soon reached the peak of Lion Rock!

programme.title: Nezha
programme.desc: A former top team racing driver wants to prove himself in a race but accidentally hurts his teammate Lily, leading to the teams downfall. When an inexperienced virtual car racing champion joins the team and unexpectedly shines in a real-life race, can the three drivers team up to regain glory for their team?

programme.title: The Eye 2
programme.desc: Joey looks to start a new life after a failed suicide attempt but finds herself pregnant and dare not tell her ex-boyfriend. At the same time, she realizes that a mysterious woman is stalking her and begins to hallucinate, leading to a nervous breakdown. Taking advice from an abbot, Joey decides to uncover the truth in order to protect her baby...

programme.title: Sex and the Beauties
programme.desc: It is said that Hong Kong is a sexy and sexual city where life is breathtakingly fast but glamorous. Fear of marriage, single & successful psychiatrist, Selina and other beauties seek for love and happy endings.

programme.title: Septet: The Story of Hong Kong
programme.desc: Seven of Hong Kong's most revered directors, all with distinctly unique styles, come together for the first time to compose a symphony of stories for their city from the 50s to the future.

programme.title: Wolf Pack
programme.desc: The Wolf Pack squad led by Lao Diao, is a foreign-based team that specializes in overseas security jobs. In one of the missions, the squad discovers that a terrorist force is planning to destroy the countrys energy source. Lao Diao is now entrusted with the task of leading his squad to fight back. Can the Wolf Pack save the day?

programme.title: Chinese Odyssey 2002
programme.desc: Set in Ming Dynasty, young Emperor Zheng De escapes from the palace with his sister who disguised as a man. They run into a notorious wanderer who runs a restaurant with his boyish sister in Jiang Nan. The two pairs of siblings from vastly different social classes descend into an inescapable swirl of gender confusion, slapstick antics and love.

programme.title: Adventure of the King
programme.desc: The Ming Emperor Zhengde flees the palace to see the world after his mother orders him to marry an ugly princess. He disguises as a commoner and escapes with his advisors, but a gambling mishap causes them to part ways and Zhengde lost all his money. Phoenix, the owner of Lung Fung Inn, takes him in out of pity, and thus begins his new adventure...

programme.title: Black Ransom
programme.desc: Mann, an accomplished police officer, has allowed his career to wane after his wife was murdered by the mafia. However, Mann is forced to return to his former glory when he is assigned to investigate a former police inspector suspected to be kidnapping mafia bosses and demanding ransoms in exchange for their lives.

programme.title: Schemes in Antiques
programme.desc: Despite his familys expertise in ancient Chinese relics, Xu Yuan becomes an electronics shop owner to distance himself from his disgraced family. However, when an antique is to be returned to China, Xu Yuan uncovers an ancient mystery and soon embarks on a journey that can finally restore his familys reputation but may also cost him his life.

programme.title: The Brotherhood of Rebel
programme.desc: Chai, a triad member, helps his childhood friend Meow flee Hong Kong after discovering that Meow attempted to kill his triad boss. 17 years later, Chai becomes a key member of the triad. When he runs into Meow one day, he knows that his gang will kill Meow if they find him. Caught between triad and brotherhood, what will Chai choose?

programme.title: Fight Back to School II
programme.desc: Star Chow (Stephen Chow) is an officer in the Royal Hong Kong Police's elite Special Duties Unit (SDU). During a meeting with his senior officer, Inspector Yip (Deanie Ip), Star jokingly suggests he wish to be reassigned to the traffic unit. Star immediately finds himself demoted to Constable engaging in traffic duty on the streets of Hong Kong. After being made the scapegoat for a failed high school terrorist investigation, Star hastily resigns from the police. He decides to enroll at the high school to launch his own private investigation. But Star realises the investigation won't be easy when he discovers that the bumbling, incompetent CID detective Tat (Ng Man Tat) is also undercover at the high school.

programme.title: The Fate of Reunion
programme.desc: Thousands of years ago, Green Snake gained enlightenment under the guidance of Dao Qing and gradually falls for him. However, her devotion to Dao Qing caused him to reincarnate and go through the pains of death. Since then, she sets out to search for the many reincarnations of Dao Qing over hundreds of years to help him reverse the situation

programme.title: The Shepherd Girl
programme.desc: In this musical drama, Hsiu Hsiu, a beautiful shepherd girl, falls in love with a handsome boatman Ta Lung. However, she cannot afford to marry him because of her fathers towering debt from gambling. To complicate the matter, a rival suitor promises to pay off all her father's debts on one condition: that Hsiu Hsiu marries him...

programme.title: Danger has Two Faces
programme.desc: Many years ago, Inspector Kam killed an innocent man and decided to resign from the police force. He became a professional killer who disguises as a pet store owner. When his best friend, Bobby begins investigating recent murder cases committed by Kam, he discovers that the mastermind behind these cases is actually his superintendent.

programme.title: Guess Who Killed My Twelve Lovers?
programme.desc: Jenny Hu, Shaw Brothers' gorgeous Chinese-German star, was given her first comedy role in the wild and wacky Guess Who Killed My Twelve Lovers? Described as "a comedy of belly laughs and chilling murders", it is a unique entry in the Hong Kong theater of the absurd.

programme.title: The Bells of Death
programme.desc: Wei Fu is an unremarkable woodcutter. However, when psychotic marauders killed his family and abducted his sister, he goes through vigorous martial arts training with an expert swordsman in order to exact revenge on the evildoers.

programme.title: Family Light Affair
programme.desc: Alfred Cheung Kin-ting returns to the screen with this seriocomic look at the clash of cultures which result when a Mainland Chinese peasant brings his family to Hong Kong. Family Light Affair, whose Chinese title literally translates as "City Lights", is the director/writer's warm-hearted memoir of street life back in the early 1980s, featuring an eclectic cast of pop music and kung fu stars who shine in their poignant roles.

programme.title: The Kung-fu Instructor
programme.desc: Wong Yang is a famous martial artist who is forced to teach kung fu to the Mong Clan, an evil clan which is trying to destroy its nemesis, the Chow Clan. Chow Ping from the Chow Clan is a student of Wongs caught in the Mongs territory and as punishment, the Mong Clan wants to cut off Chow Pings limbs. Wong steps in to defend his student.

programme.title: Tropicana Interlude
programme.desc: Ping and Su are lovers who operate a travel agency specializing in Southeast Asian holidays. Tung, a school mistress, and her students join a guided tour lead by Ping. During the trip, a spoiled kid Li is attracted to Ping but Su thinks Ping has fallen for Tung and leaves. How will Ping deal with the situation and ends up happily back with Su?

programme.title: Kid From Kwangtung
programme.desc: After many years as a respected actor and action choreographer, the Shaw Studio finally gave the dependable and commendable Hsu Hsia a chance to direct his own movies. He didn't waste the opportunity, inviting three other kung-fu designers to help on this fight-filled thriller. Wang Yu, co-star of such classics as Dirty Ho and The Kid With A Tattoo, here takes center stage as a young rascal caught between an anti-Ching Confederation and violent, vengeful Ching troops. But when he discovers that the good guys are led by master martial arts actor Jen Shih-kuan and the bad guys are led by the incredible Huang Cheng-li everyone knows that loads of great kung-fu is in store.

programme.title: Tales of Larceny
programme.desc: Connecting all the antics of bosses, monks, beggars, and thieves is the slippery and sinuous efforts of three pickpockets so adept at their chosen skill that they can even trick three beauties of their underwear without missing a step.

programme.title: What Price Honesty
programme.desc: In this period martial arts thriller, three police graduates are assigned to a town rife with crimes and corruption. They vow to uphold justice but are hampered by their corrupt superior, resulting in them putting their lives and the lives of their beloved in danger.

programme.title: The Secret Of The Dirk
programme.desc: The inhabitants of the City of Liu are forced to flee when the vicious Black Tigers gang raids their city, but are able to hide all their gold and treasures in a valley. A team of swordswomen led by Liu wants to get their hands on the treasures before the bandits, but both parties will have to contend with the wandering swordsman Chou for them...

programme.title: Torrent Of Desire
programme.desc: Rich playboy David is a drunk until he falls in love with a fashion model Dan Feng and marries her. David's sister Mona is in love with his best friend Han Ming, who rejected her as he secretly loves Dan Feng as well. Out of jealousy and hatred, Mona lies to David about a fake affair between Han Ming and Dan Feng...

programme.title: Tales of a Eunuch
programme.desc: Tales Of A Eunuch reunites the potent mix of martial arts superstar Gordon Liu, who plays Emperor in cognito Kang Hsi, with the kung-fu comedienne Wang Yu, an anti-Ching revolutionary. It is a film laced with wild barrages of excellent martial arts chiefly choreographed by Yuen Hua and Yuan Pien; Jackie Chan's long-time kung-fu classmates. At one time, Wang was considered to be the next Alexander Fu Sheng.

programme.title: Passing Flickers
programme.desc: This film is an amusing insiders look at the Hong Kong film industry and is based on Director Li Han Hsiangs popular newspaper column recounting his work at Shaw Brothers. The collection of some of his funniest and most surreal film musings of the era, filled with behind-the-scene asides, this is a must-see for any Hong Kong cinema aficionado!

programme.title: The 14 Amazons
programme.desc: The Yang family had served their country in Song Dynasty for generations. When General Yang is ambushed and killed during the war in Jin Shan, the grand matriarch led the entire family to take revenge and defend the country.

programme.title: Spring Blossoms
programme.desc: Some of Shaw Brothers' biggest female stars of the 1970s share the screen in this tale of young love and interfering parents, starring Lily Li, Shu Pei Pei and Essie Lin Chia.

programme.title: Lady Of Steel
programme.desc: A young swordswoman Fang Ying Qi sets out to join the Flying Dragon Clan in their defense against the invading Jin forces. Fang also intends to avenge the murder of her parents by bandit leader Han 20 years ago. Han has since taken on a false identity as a member of the Flying Dragon Clan and Fang must rely on her deadly sword skills to stop Han.

programme.title: The Adulteress
programme.desc: The film is about the drugged, then disgraced wife of a peddler in the waning days of the Ching Dynasty. To make matters worse, shes soon framed for her husbands murder by her rapist, the son of the local magistrate! And even that is not the end of her woes in this emotional suspense

programme.title: Vengeance is a Golden Blade
programme.desc: Convoy Master Lis wife has an affair with his rival Long, who plans to steal Lis Golden Blade and kill him as well as his young daughter. Li and his daughter manage to escape and the latter grows up to be a skilled swordswoman who vows to avenge her mothers death a lie told by Li. The truth is revealed when she sees her mother alive by chance.

programme.title: Three Sinners
programme.desc: Based on the classic Ming Dynasty novel The Water Margin, Three Sinners is a Huangmei Opera about love, betrayal, murder, and redemption. Starring Hong Kong's premiere movie couple, it is one of the grandest Eastmancolor-Shawscope costume musicals in the Shaw Brothers library.

programme.title: The Anonymous Heroes
programme.desc: In this action comedy, two young men join a rebel group after the Chinese Revolution of 1911 and accidentally become patriotic heroes. Assisted by a warlords daughter, they successfully help the rebels steal weapons from the warlord.

programme.title: Rose, Be My Love
programme.desc: Not a love triangle but a love 'rectangle', Rose, Be My Love is a romantic drama set on the eve of World War II that represents the high standards achieved by Shaw Brothers in both aspects of star power and technical polish.

programme.title: The Web of Death
programme.desc: To rule the martial arts world, the Head of the Snake Sect seeks to possess a deadly plant called Five Poison Web, spreading rumours on its whereabouts. Brothers Xiong and Kit are sent to investigate. Xiong falls in love with Su who has a clue of where the plant is, but she accidentally hurts Kit when seeking the plant, devastating Xiong.

programme.title: Return of the Phoenix
programme.desc: An imperial minister Cheng betroths his pretty younger daughter, Ye, to his friend's son, Mu. His wife however, refuses to let Ye marry before her elder daughter Yan, who is ugly and undesirable. Yan is asked to pretend as Ye to meet Mu but scares him away. A rich guy who likes Ye meanwhile pretends as Mu to attend the wedding...

programme.title: The Reckless Cricket
programme.desc: Inspired by Drunken Master, this kung fu comedy features a bumbling martial artist creating a cricket-style fighting arts to fight and defeat the different martial artists who have beaten him before.

programme.title: The Merry Wife
programme.desc: A 17-year old schoolgirl marries her 35-year-old teacher. Comedy ensues when they attempt to keep their relationship a secret despite being in the same school. When they discover unwanted suitors going after their other halves, jealousy threatens to expose their marriage any minute!

programme.title: The Knight of Knights
programme.desc: Wen Su Chen, the leader of seven knights, sends his six sworn brothers to investigate a monastery. Unfortunately, they are killed by an abbot who plans to murder Inspector Lin. Wen saved Lin and battles the abbot to avenge his dead sworn brothers. With Lin and his armys help, they bring down the ruthless monks in the monastery.

programme.title: Big Times for the Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: Ah Niu finds a bag of jewels on the street and becomes rich. It is at this time that Uncle Zhou asks him to sign a contract to marry a girl, but it turns out to be a trap for Ah Niu to sell his house. In the end, Ah Niu becomes poor again

programme.title: The Silent Swordsman
programme.desc: This is adapted from Louis Chas The Book and the Sword. A young swordsman is tasked to lead a patriotic secret society to fight the traitorous general who colludes with the enemy. At the same time, he encounters a female warrior and two beautiful princesses, and is caught between all their affections for him.

programme.title: The Venus' Tear Diamond
programme.desc: Legendary rival jewel thieves Fragrant Night and Nocturnal Earl travel to Japan to steal the famous Venus Tear Diamond. They fall quickly in love at first sight, without knowing the other person is their rival and is after the same prize. Who will get the diamond, and will it mean the end of their new found love?

programme.title: The Duel of the Century
programme.desc: A duel has been arranged at the Forbidden City between two formidable swordsmen of the martial world, Ye Gu Cheng and Xi Men Chui Xue. Lu Xiao Feng smells something fishy about the duel as the two swordsmen never met and do not have any conflicts. He decides to investigate more with Hua Man Lou, and eventually uncovers some hidden conspiracies

programme.title: Beyond the Great Wall
programme.desc: Wang Zhao Jun refuses to bribe the imperial painter, so he draws an ugly portrait of her, preventing her from being selected by the Emperor until they meet in person. The painter ends up in exile and plots for Wang to marry the Huns warlord as a revenge. The Emperor rejects this, provoking a war which is only averted when Wang sacrifices herself.

programme.title: Heroes Shed No Tears
programme.desc: Kao Chien Fei is a young swordsman who wields a special sword with a teardrop marked on its blade. He is charged with averting an impending crisis in the martial arts world, but the villain, Zhou Tung Lai, wishes to become the ruler in the martial arts world, and launches a scheme to pit the various heroes against one another.

programme.title: Tragic Commitment
programme.desc: When the husband of a doctor, Tung is fatally wounded in an accident, he reveals to her about his affair with Blackie, who is impregnated with his baby. Despite the devastation of the betrayal and the eventual death of her husband, Tung is pressured by her mother-in-law into putting up with Blackie and offer $1M for her baby...

programme.title: The Cave of Silken Web
programme.desc: In this third instalment of Shaw Brothers Journey to the West, Monk Tang San Zang is trapped by seven seductive spider spirits who are hell-bent on achieving immortality by eating him! Monkey, Pigsy and Sha Wu Jing have to fight the spider spirits to rescue Monk Tang San Zang.

programme.title: Jonah Hex
programme.desc: Oscar nominee Josh Brolin plays Jonah Hex, a scarred drifter and bounty hunter who can track down anyone...and anything. Having survived death, Jonah's violent history is steeped in myth and legend - leaving him with one foot in the natural world and one on the "other side." His only human connection is with Lilah (Transformers' Megan Fox), whose life in a brothel has left her with scars of her own. But Jonah's past is about to catch up with him when the U.S. military makes him an offer he can't refuse: in exchange for his freedom, he must track down and stop the dangerous terrorist Quentin Turnbull (Oscar nominee John Malkovich). But Turnbull, who is gathering an army and preparing to unleash Hell, is also Jonah's oldest enemy and will stop at nothing until Jonah is dead. Based on the legendary graphic novel, this epic adventure thriller gives a new face to the comic book genre by combining the Western genre with supernatural elements.
